Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:15.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Using Caesar's bandana,\NJoJo barely defeated Wamuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:25.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Lisa Lisa faced off against Kars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:35.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Von Stroheim and Speedwagon\Nappeared suddenly with help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:42.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, in a cowardly turn,\NKars used a double to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:46.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He sprang out and\Nstabbed Lisa Lisa in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:51.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo and Lisa Lisa are in\Nthe greatest peril of their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:58.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kars, you bastard!\NI hope you rot in hell forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:05.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know that\Nthat woman is his own mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let go, JoJo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:27.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a forest of crystal spikes below.\NShe'd die instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kars!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul is as rotten as a pumpkin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:37.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,left in a field that even flies won't visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:43.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shout at me. Grumble at me. Insult me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:48.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,While you're holding that rope,\Nthat's all you can really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:09.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the silent depths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:16.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The pillars awaken from ages-long sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:24.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:31.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Summons the valorous to stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:39.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If inherited love is called fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:45.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then take another step with smiling eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:52.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mystify the darkness, dodge in a blink
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid the blade,\Nfind an opening and strike
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:03:01.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Conviction tested\Nopens the way to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bloody storm\NHot like a bloody stone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:10.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny written into your veins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:16.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The undying bonds of honor arise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:21.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take hold of them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:31.17,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 24: The Ties that Bind JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo! Lisa Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:09.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo doesn't realize\Nhis mother's life is in his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Speedwagon, we should tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:14.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:22.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Von Stroheim, are you done\Nwith the vampires?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have to help JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:30.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think we can get rid of them\Nin just a minute or two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:38.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. They need more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:55.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, the rope will slip\Nif you don't watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:08.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,While you're holding the rope,\Nyour hasty feet can only move so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:16.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He kicked Kars,\Nbut Hamon didn't flow into him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're in a real fix!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:23.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your Hamon is running dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:28.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You might have just enough\Nfor one last, all-out attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just stroll up to you and take
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:38.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nyour life like I'm plucking a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kars!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:50.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I might have barely enough\Nin me for one final attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not exactly confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:57.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, I've come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:01.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's something to make you choke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:04.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:05.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not tying any ropes together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a match!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:15.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think I'll do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is JoJo up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He set his scarf on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before this fire burns me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:32.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use all I've got \Nleft to send you packing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The fire is a gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:36.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a risk to motivate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I seek life within death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An act like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...is just desperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't toy with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:59.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just dodging around\Nin order to catch your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:04.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again:\NI want to kill you at my leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't play king of the apes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now! I need to breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if I look silly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:19.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can cut Lisa Lisa's rope\Nwhenever I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And if you dodge again, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:28.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Should I cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:41.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You ran before. Now come to me, slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:47.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to cut the rope,\Nstay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:49.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's your choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:56.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is your life more precious\Nthan this woman's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're planning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut if I cut this, you'll fall as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.38,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. That's two birds with one cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This rope is connected to JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When did he do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't have the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:42.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When he first kicked, he let himself\Nbe cut along with the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,While he lit the match, he secretly tied
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:50.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nhis leg to her rope and made a loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He needed a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So he set his scarf on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And then to tie the ropes together,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:05.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nhe let Lisa Lisa be cut down on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That cunning devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're holding me and Lisa Lisa up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You deceived me, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd hear that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:26.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you like tricking,\Nbut you hate to be tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You may have lived\Nfor over 10,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:33.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But to compete with my skills,\Nyou need another decade!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your time is up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:44.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hamon Overdrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-That was the last of my Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm burned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:01.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any Hamon left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It got into him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He did it! He hit Kars with Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.38,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Off you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:53.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Kars fell into the crystal spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's finished! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:06.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hamon will travel right up his arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:10.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're weak! Your time is up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:14.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even we could finish you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:33.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to spook us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's eliminate him for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out the UV amplifier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:41.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Coach Lisa Lisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:57.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kars said he didn't quite kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:01.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he hit anything vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:10.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we act quickly,\NI'm sure you'll live through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Speedwagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:23.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:30.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Granny Erina tell JoJo\Nhis mother died when he was little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:35.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Lisa Lisa\Nhide her past from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smokey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:42.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Erina told me not to ask you,\Nbut I have to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:47.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's his mother.\NKeeping that from him is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smokey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:53.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo and Granny Erina are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:13:00.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They saved me from crooked cops,\Neven though I was just a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:05.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here!\NI'll do all I can to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Smokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:23.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You did take good care of Erina\Nwhile I was away from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:27.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But promise not to tell JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:32.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Joestar family issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:35.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIt's not our place to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:43.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The name Lisa Lisa is an alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:47.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Her real name is Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:52.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was raised by\Na Hamon-user named Straizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:14:00.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She and Erina's son, George,\Nfell in love and got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:12.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,George and Elizabeth had a son.\NYou know him as JoJo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:23.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo's father George was\Na member of the Royal Flying Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:27.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aviation developed rapidly\Nduring the First World War.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:32.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,George was among the first\Nbrave pilots to fly into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:42.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He stood out as a hero\Neven among the Royal Flying Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...a gut-wrenching horror from the past
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ncame back to haunt the Joestars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:57.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years before, Dio had created\Nblood-sucking zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:03.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Straizo, myself and the others\Nthought we had exterminated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:10.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But one had escaped, hid within society,\Nand lived for decades undiscovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was a cunning, intelligent creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He created no spawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:27.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He ate even the bones and hair\Nof his victims, leaving no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:39.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And by some wicked twist of fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:45.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...he worked as a commander\Nin the Royal Flying Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-The Royal Flying Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:49.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWith JoJo's dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:54.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,George uncovered his secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He had listened well to Straizo and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:01.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But ultimately,\NGeorge was an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:07.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He had character and talent,\Nbut he hadn't trained with Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before he could unmask the commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:15.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nhe was discovered and attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:19.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His message to Straizo wasn't in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:29.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,George's death was covered up\Nas a nighttime plane crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:38.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Straizo and I found this suspicious,\Nand eventually found the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:47.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That night, I told Elizabeth\Nas she held an infant JoJo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:53.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of showing grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...she flew out of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:14.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was a genius with Hamon,\Nbut her emotions consumed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:20.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was witnessed\Nwhen she killed the commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:28.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The military didn't know\Nabout zombies or Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:36.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They concluded that Elizabeth\Nhad attacked their beloved commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,killed him, and burned his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:43.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soon she was known around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:47.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nas a murderer and national traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:09.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We used all the Speedwagon Foundation's\Nresources to cover her trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Elizabeth had to leave England behind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,without even a word to her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:23.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina knew what had happened,\Nand she had a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:28.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When this child grows up\Nand asks about his parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...please tell him they both died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:49.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so Elizabeth became Lisa Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At least say his mother is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know painfully well why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:10.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina lost her husband and son in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe battle between Hamon and the masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:17.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But thinking of her grandson, of JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:21.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...she didn't want Hamon in his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa is the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Such a tragic family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Such a miserable fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:47.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo used Hamon\Nto save his mother's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Speedwagon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:59.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's no reason\Nfor Lisa Lisa to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:04.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo knows about Hamon,\Nand he used it to save his mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:10.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:14.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have to know how Erina\Nand Lisa Lisa feel first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:16.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:23.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Aim it right at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:26.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We will have the honor\Nof executing Kars!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:36.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die, Kars!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:41.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you how good it feels\Nto order this myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, von Stroheim! The mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:07.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Stone is in his mask!\NUV light will help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:09.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:13.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't fire the UV amplifier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:43.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't see him holding the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see him put the Red Stone in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:49.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dear God...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kars...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:40.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate life form...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:43.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He can manipulate life at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:45.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no way to stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:49.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kars, the Ultimate Thing, is born!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:51.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 25: The Birth of a Superbeing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:53.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
